                       Check-list
                       ==========

1. passport - original (if old available and latest one)
2. passport scanned pages of latest one including visa entry and exit stamps other countries
3. Aadhaar card.
4. If person is employee:
     - employment proof
     - NOC
     - leave letter
     - 6 months bank statements
     - 3 months pay-slips
     - 3 years IT Returns
     - additional income (rent,agriculture etc, per month)
     - covering letter
     - proof of ties to India to show you'll return.
5. If person is self-employee:
     - financial proof like 6 months of bank statements (personal & business)
     - 3 years IT Returns (personal & business)
     - business registration/accountant's letter
     - partnership deed.
     - GST of company
     - additional income (rent,agriculture etc, per month)
     - strong cover letter on company letterhead
     - proof of ties to India to show you'll return. 
